The paper discusses the vulnerability of deep learning models to adversarial attacks and proposes a method to improve the capability to resist steganalysis of steganographic schemes. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of computer security (cs.CR), computer vision and pattern recognition (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), multimedia (cs.MM), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Among these, cs.CR and cs.CV are the most likely sub-categories as the paper focuses on the security and analysis of images.
